          "jdk.unsupported=${file("src/testPatch/java").absolutePath}"
      ])
  }
  
  tasks.named("test") {
      dependsOn("compileSunReflectPatch")
      jvmArgs("--patch-module", "jdk.unsupported=${sunReflectPatchClasses.get().asFile.absolutePath}")
